com.davidjarski.vfatreader

Class Disk

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.davidjarski.vfatreader.Disk

  • public class Disk
extends java.lang.Object
    A Disk contains a reference to a FAT12 disk image and provides methods for reading the image. To facilitate analysis of the FAT file system, the read() methods have corresponding readToString() versions that return a hex dump of the bytes read.

    Writing to the disk image is not a supported feature.
    Author:
    David Jarski (c) 2014-07-31
